		"LoadingTip_1"                 "Use Joker Coins to draw cosmetics from the inventory in the top menu."
		"LoadingTip_2"                 "At the end of a game round, players who either clear more than 30 stages in Solo Mode or achieve a high ranking in Duo Mode will be rewarded with Joker Coins (up to 30 per day)."
		"LoadingTip_3"                 "At the end of the last day of each month, ranks are finalized, and top-ranked players are rewarded with Joker Coins."
		"LoadingTip_4"                 "Double-click a player‘s hero icon (on the Betting page, Top Plays page, or Duel Recap page) to quickly snap the camera to that hero."
		"LoadingTip_5"                 "If the duel time expires without a clear winner, victory is awarded to the player with the higher percentage of health remaining."
		"LoadingTip_6"                 "If a player wins the duel but no one else has bet on them, they claim the entire prize pool."
		"LoadingTip_7"                 "Starting from Round 15, some screeps will possess True Sight."
		"LoadingTip_8"                 "Perseverance can be upgraded into an Azure Lance, significantly increasing spell damage."
		"LoadingTip_9"                 "If you have more gold than you can spend, you can purchase Attribute Tomes from the shop."
		"LoadingTip_10"                "If you wish to hide a specific skill from other players, you can use a Void Scroll."
		"LoadingTip_11"                "After rounds 10, 20, 30, and 40, the player with the lowest net worth receives a free Book of Relearning."
		"LoadingTip_12"                "When the round timer expires, creeps will enter a Rage state, gaining increased damage, movement/attack speed, and the ability to Sunder Armor."
		"LoadingTip_13"                "For players who throw duels (intentionally lose), hold ALT and click on their hero's avatar to mark them as a thrower."
		"LoadingTip_14"                "Press the hotkey F8 to drag and reorder skills in your skill bar."
		"LoadingTip_15"                "If your skill hotkeys become missing, you can purchase a Void Scroll to restore them."
		"LoadingTip_16"                "Single-player: Use【-suicide】to die and end the round, scoring as-is."
		"LoadingTip_17"                "PASS players can freely choose any hero in the PVE mode (the single-player challenge mode)."
		"LoadingTip_18"                "Players with a quit rate >20% will be flagged as \"Leavers\" and will not earn free Joker Coins upon completing a game. This status persists until their quit rate drops below 20% or until the current season ends."
		"LoadingTip_19"                "After an early quit, you will not earn Funny Coins for that match. A victory will not increase your ranking points (but a loss will still decrease it). Your quitting hero will be taken over by an AI bot for the remainder of the game."
		"LoadingTip_20"                "The Mask of Domination can be upgraded into the Mask of Supremacy, greatly enhancing the attributes of summoned units."
		"LoadingTip_21"                "Duel participants receive a free bet equal to 10% of the total prize pool (placed on themselves). Upon winning the duel, they receive an additional 10% of the prize pool as a bonus."
