		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_imba_essence_aura_buff"							         	    "Essence Aura"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_imba_essence_aura_buff_Description"						        "Casting a spell will recover part of your total mana"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_essence_aura_datadriven"					    "Essence Aura"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_essence_aura_datadriven_Description"		    "Whenever Outworld Devourer or his nearby allies casts a spell, it restores a percentage of its mana pool."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_essence_aura_datadriven_Lore"					"The crystals of the Outworld produce arcane power, and the Harbinger channels it into the world of mortals."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_essence_aura_datadriven_restore_amount"		"%RESTORE MANA:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_essence_aura_datadriven_bonus_mana"			"EXTRA MANA:"
