		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_hero_refreshing"                                     "Fountain Aura"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_hero_refreshing_Description"                         "Invulnerable. Increase health and mana regen speed. Increase ability cooldown speed by 100%%."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_creature_berserk"                                    "Rage"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_creature_berserk_Description"                        "Round time expired. Creature grant bounus speed and damage. Attack will tear enemy armor."

