		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_kaya_2_lua"				            	"Sky Staff"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_kaya_2_lua_Description"				    "<h1>Passive：Sky Staff</h1>Every Intelligence provide %spell_amplify%%% Spell Amplification<br><br>Has no effect on percentage-based damage spells. <br><br>Only 20%% effectiveness on other heroes in duels. "
