		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_trueshot_lua"								"Precision Aura"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_trueshot_lua_Description"					"Adds bonus damage to the physical attack of allied, <font color='#FF7800'>ranged</font> Hero units based on a percentage of Drow's agility.Affects creeps for 30 seconds when cast."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_trueshot_lua_Lore"						"Traxex' time spent alone in the forests of her Drow home has allowed her to teach other archers how to improve their bow skills."
