		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua"												"Eclipse"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_Lore"										"In times of great need, Selemene herself descends into the world, blocking out the light and hope of the opposed."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_Description"									"Showers random nearby enemies with strikes of Lucent Beam. These beams do not stun their targets, and there is a maximum number of times that a single target can be struck. Also turns day into night for %duration_tooltip% seconds."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_Note0"										"Eclipse work if without Lucent Beam."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_Note1"										"Beams will stop if Luna is killed."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_Note2"										"Will not hit invisible units."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_Note3"										"There is a %beam_interval% seconds gap between beams, %beam_interval_scepter% seconds with scepter."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_beams"										"TOTAL BEAMS:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_damage"										"LUCENT BEAM'S BASIC DAMAGE:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_hit_count"									"MAX BEAMS PER UNIT:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_radius"										"RADIUS:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_abilityduration"								"Eclipse Duration: "
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_scepter_description"							"Luna can cast Eclipse on an allied unit or herself, causing the Eclipse effect to follow the target, or cast it on an area. Additionally, it increases the number of Lucent Beams, extends the Eclipse duration, removes the maximum number of strikes per target, and halves the interval between Lucent Beam spawns."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_ability_note"								"If you have learned Lucent Beam or Lucent Beam [Frosthaven], Eclipse will deal damage based on whichever deals more damage, and it will inherit the area damage effect of Lucent Beam [Frosthaven]."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_lua_night_duration"								"Night Duration: "
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_luna_eclipse_lua"											"Eclipse"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_luna_eclipse_lua_Description"								"Strikes nearby targets with Lucent Beam."

		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua"						        "Jingu Mastery"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_Description"			        "Monkey King's attacks awaken the Jingu Bang's power. Upon the fourth hit on the same enemy hero, Monkey King earns four charged attacks that have bonus damage and lifesteal."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_Lore"					        "Always sensitive to the moods of its master, the Jingu Bang radiates power when Sun Wukong's combat fervor is on full display."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_Note0"					        "Hitting an enemy with Boundless Strike adds to the hit counter."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_Note1"					        "Repeatedly hitting an enemy refreshes the Jingu Mastery debuff duration."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_Note2"					        "Hit charges on enemies cannot be dispelled."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_required_hits"			        "REQUIRED HITS:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_counter_duration"		        "COUNTER DURATION:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_charges"				        "CHARGES:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_bonus_damage"			        "BONUS DAMAGE:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_lifesteal"				        "%BONUS LIFESTEAL:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_buff"				            "Jingu Mastery"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_modifier_monkey_king_jingu_mastery_lua_count_debuff"			"Jingu Mastery"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_fire_lua"							"Liquid Fire"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_fire_lua_Description"				"Jakiro burns his enemies in an area of effect with fire added to his attack, while slowing their attacks."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_fire_lua_Lore"						"The left maw of Jakiro opens, laying waste to any in its path."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_fire_lua_Note0"						"Works on both units and buildings."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_fire_lua_slow_attack_speed_pct"		"ATTACK SLOW:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_fire_lua_damage"					"BURN DAMAGE:"
