		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ranged_cleave_2_lore"                "Many wonder how a 4-feet tall grandma can survive the ferocious beasts of the Outlands. The answer is simple - Beatrix's triple-barreled monstrosity, more siege weapon than shotgun, which she calls her 'boomstick'."
