		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dazzle_good_juju_lua"									            "Good Juju"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dazzle_good_juju_lua_Description"						            "Whenever Dazzle Casts a Spell, all other abilities currently on cooldown have their cooldowns reduced."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dazzle_good_juju_lua_scepter_Description"				            "Good Juju reduces all item Cooldowns by %item_cooldown_reduction%%% and becomes an active ability that can be cast on allied units to refresh all item cooldowns."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dazzle_good_juju_lua_Lore"							            "Each spell cast from the Void Realm allows it to further penetrate the surrounding world."
