		// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua_ability_note"						"<font color='#B694FF'>射手天赋</font>的<font color='#B694FF'>阿哈利姆神杖</font>可由<font color='#B694FF'>近战英雄</font>使用。<br><font color='#B694FF'>射手天赋</font>的额外敏捷光环效果不会影响<font color='#B694FF'>近战英雄</font>。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua"										"Marksmanship"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua_Description"							"Drow's experiences in battle grant her a chance to launch arrows with incredible accuracy and effectiveness. Pierces through the enemy's defenses, ignoring their base armor. Grants Drow and nearby ranged heroes with bonus agility based on Drow's current agility. This ability is disabled if there is an enemy hero within %disable_range% range."
		// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua_scepter_Description"					"使卓尔游侠的攻击分裂出额外的箭矢，攻击主目标附近单位，造成较少的伤害。"
