		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua_Lore"								"The Drow Ranger is the epitome of archery prowess."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua_Note0"								"Marksmanship procs have true strike."
