		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua"							"Sanity's Eclipse"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_Description"				"Unleashes a psychic blast that deals to enemies based on the difference between your mana and the target's mana. Sanity's Eclipse can hit units trapped by Astral Imprisonment."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_Lore"						"When an Outworld crystal ruptures, cataclysmic energies are released, and the reverberations of this power are felt interdimensionally."
