		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pudge_flesh_heap_lua"                                    "Flesh Heap"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pudge_flesh_heap_lua_note0"                              "Stacks counted upon acquiring the ability are calculated by adding the hero's kills and assists and therefore may give extra stacks."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pudge_flesh_heap_lua_Description"                        "Gives Pudge a guaranteed damage block against all types of attack. Passively grants bonus strength that increases each time Pudge kills an enemy Hero or it dies in his vicinity.Flesh Heap is retroactive, meaning it can gain charges before it is skilled, which then become active."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pudge_flesh_heap_lua_Lore"                               "The Butcher gives new meaning to the words 'meat shield.'"
