		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_ability_note"						        "Attacking creeps also provides bonus Agility."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua"											"Essence Shift"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_Description"								"Slark steals the life essence of enemy heroes with his attacks, draining each of their attributes and converting them to bonus Agility. If Slark kills an affected enemy hero, he permanently steals <font color='#ffffff'><b>1</b></font> Agility."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_Lore"										"With each strike at his adversaries, Slark's knowledge of their weaknesses improves."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_Note0"									"Attributes cannot be dropped below 1."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_Note1"									"Essence Shifted stats are returned to normal on death. The stat return for Slark and for the affected hero are separate."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_Note2"									"To permanently steal Agility, Slark doesn't need to land the killing blow, as long as the enemy hero is killed within 300 range of Slark while having the Essence Shift debuff."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_agi_gain"									"HERO AGILITY GAINED:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_creep_agi_gain"							"Agility Gained From Creeps: "
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_stat_loss"								"ALL ATTRIBUTE LOSS:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_essence_shift_lua_duration"									"AGI DURATION:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_slark_essence_shift_lua_agi"										"Essence Shift"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_slark_essence_shift_lua_agi_Description"							"Gaining %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_STATS_AGILITY_BONUS% agility."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_slark_essence_shift_lua_agi_permenant"							"Essence Shift"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_slark_essence_shift_lua_agi_permenant_Description"				"Gaining %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_STATS_AGILITY_BONUS% agility permanently."

		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_depth_shroud_lua"				"Depth Shroud"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_slark_depth_shroud_lua_Description"  "Creates a cloud at the target location. All allies inside the radius are hidden and affected by Shadow Dance."
