		//Undying
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_tombstone_lua"                             "Tombstone"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_tombstone_lua_Description"                 "Summons a tombstone at the target point. Zombies will frequently spawn next to every enemy unit in the area around the Tombstone, and attack them. Zombies have the Deathlust ability, which causes their attacks to slow the target, and if the target reaches below a certain amount of health, increases the attack and movement speed of the zombie."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_tombstone_lua_radius"                      "Zombie Spawn Radius:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_tombstone_lua_zombie_interval"             "Zombie Spawn Interval:"
