		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_tombstone_lua_ability_note"		                     	""

		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_decay_lua"                                                "Decay"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_decay_lua_Description"                                    "Undying steals strength from all enemies in an area, dealing damage as he claims the enemy's strength for himself. Deals %creep_damage_mult%%% damage to creeps."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_decay_lua_Lore"                                           "The strength of the living is simply borrowed from the strength of the dead."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_decay_lua_Note0"                                          "The strength stolen stacks, but can't cause a hero to have strength below 1."
