		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zeus_static_field_lua"						"Static Field(OLD)"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zeus_static_field_lua_Description"			"Zeus shocks all nearby enemy units whenever he casts a spell, causing damage proportional to their current health. This effect procs once per %shock_duration% seconds on each enemy when triggered by non-Zeus abilities.<br>Non-Zeus abilities deal %nonzeus_multiplier%%% of Static Field damage on proc."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zeus_static_field_lua_shard_description"		"Static Field can be cast to perform a Heavenly Jump, shocking the closest visible enemy (prioritizing heroes) within 2000 range, dealing Static Field damage to them and reducing their movement speed by 100% for 2.5 seconds. If Zeus was moving forward, he will jump towards that direction. Cooldown: 11. Manacost: 100."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zeus_static_field_lua_Lore"					"The air crackles with static when the Thundergod walks the world."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zeus_static_field_lua_Note0"					"Toggle abilities nor abilities with zero cooldown doesn't trigger Static Field."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zeus_static_field_lua_Note1"					"Using items doesn't trigger Static Field."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zeus_static_field_lua_damage_health_pct"		"%HEALTH REDUCTION:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_zeus_static_field_shock_lua"					"Shocked by Static Field"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_static_field_ability_note"	           "Only <font color='#B694FF'>Arc Lightning, Lightning Bolt, Heavenly Jump, Thundergods Wrath</font> can trigger Static Field."
		"econ_season_2020_5"                                                "2020 May Limited"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_warlock_fatal_bonds_lua"							"Fatal Bonds"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_warlock_fatal_bonds_lua_Description"				"Binds several enemy units together, causing a percentage of the damage dealt to one of them to be felt by the others."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_warlock_fatal_bonds_lua_Lore"						"An ancient incantation that links the vital energies of multiple lifeforms into one collective body."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_warlock_fatal_bonds_lua_count"					"ENEMIES BOUND:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_warlock_fatal_bonds_lua_damage_share_percentage"	"%SHARED DAMAGE:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_warlock_fatal_bonds_lua_duration"					"DURATION:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_warlock_fatal_bonds_lua_Note0"					"The shared damage type is the same as the type of damage inflicted."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_fatal_bonds_debuff"						     	"Fatal Bonds"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_fatal_bonds_debuff_Description"				    "Distributing %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%% of all damage to linked units"

