		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack"	                "Geminate Attack [Frosthaven]"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_Description"	    "Allows Weaver to dispatch two attacks at once.<font color='#70EA72'>The second attack targets several enemies, as well as Weaver's primary target.</font>"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_Lore"	        "Skitskurr's relationship with time is somewhat variable, causing his actions to be witnessed - and felt - more than once."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_Note0"	        "The second attack leaves Weaver 0.25 seconds after the first, and has no range limit."
