		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua"                                "Requiem of Souls"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Description"                    "Shadow Fiend gathers his captured souls to release them as lines of demonic energy. Units near Shadow Fiend when the souls are released can be damaged by several lines of energy. Any unit damaged by Requiem of Souls movement speed and damage will be reduced for %requiem_slow_duration% seconds for each line hit. Number of Lines of energy is 18. <br><br> Requiem of Souls is automatically cast whenever Shadow Fiend dies, regardless of its cooldown."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_aghanim_description"            "Increases Max Souls and causes Requiem of Souls to return back to Shadow Fiend. The wave back to Shadow Fiend deals less damage, but heals Shadow Fiend for all the damage it dealt."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_ability_note"                   "Not require <font color='#B694FF'>Necromastery</font>. Release fixed 18 lines (23 lines with Scepter)."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_abilitycastpoint"               "CAST DELAY:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_reduction_ms"           "%MOVEMENT REDUCTION:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_reduction_damage"       "%DAMAGE REDUCTION"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_damage_pct_scepter"     "%SCEPTER DAMAGE ON RETURN:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_heal_pct_scepter"       "%SCEPTER HEAL ON RETURN:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Lore"                           "The captured souls of those past slain are released to ravage their former allies."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note0"                          "Release fixed 18 lines (23 lines with Scepter)."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note1"                          "The movement reductions from Requiem of Souls go through spell immunity."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note2"                          "Fear and movement slow do not apply when if the Requiem was released on death."

		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua"									         "Caustic Finale"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_Description"						         "Sand King's attacks inject a venom that causes enemy units to move more slowly and to violently explode when it dies."
