		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua"										"Anchor Smash"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua_Description"							"Tidehunter swings his mighty anchor to attack and deal bonus damage to nearby enemies and reduce their attack damage."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua_Lore"									"Stolen from one of Admiral Kunkka's flagships, Leviathan's heavy anchor proves useful as a melee weapon."
