		//Visage
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua"									"Gravekeeper's Cloak"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Description"						"Visage generates a layered barrier that protects him from damage.<br><br>Layers can be removed by heroes and by creeps. Heroes remove %hero_multiplier% layers and creeps remove one. Layers take time to recover."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_shard_Description"					"Grants Visage the ability to cast Stone Form. Restores up to 35% of your health. Cooldown: 60. Manacost: 125."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Lore"								"Visage's tough scales share equal properties of ghost and stone, making it nearly impervious to blade and magical assault."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Note0"								"Each time Visage receives damage greater than the Minimum Damage that was not self-inflicted, a layer is removed."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Note1"								"Familiars within %radius% range of Visage will receive the current damage reduction from Gravekeeper's Cloak."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_damage_reduction"					"%DAMAGE REDUCTION PER LAYER:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_max_layers"							"MAX LAYERS:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_recovery_time"						"LAYER RECOVERY TIME:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_minimum_damage"						"MINIMUM DAMAGE:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_max_damage_reduction"				"%MAX DAMAGE REDUCTION:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua"									"Gravekeeper's Cloak"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Description"						"Gaining bonus damage reduction per stack."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_secondary_lua"							"Gravekeeper's Cloak"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_secondary_lua_Description"				"Gaining damage reduction."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua"									            	"Spirits"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_Description"						              	"Summon %spirits_count% particle spirits that dance in a circle around Io. If a particle collides with an enemy hero, it explodes, damaging all enemy units in an area around it.Creeps take minor damage from touching a particle spirit, but do not cause them to explode. When its duration ends, any remaining Spirits explode."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_Lore"							            	"Io twists the particles of the universe with its unimaginable capabilities."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_Note0"							            	"After summoning, Io can call the spirits in and out."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_scepter_description"				            	"Spirits now passively spawn around Io constantly every second. Max of 5."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_creep_damage"					            	"CREEP DAMAGE:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_hero_damage"							            "HERO DAMAGE:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_max_range"							            "OSCILLATION RADIUS:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_explode_radius"						            "EXPLOSION RADIUS:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_lua_spirit_duration"					            	"DURATION:"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_in_lua"									            "Spirits Movement"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_wisp_spirits_in_lua_Description"						            "Sends the spirits closer to you. Can be toggled on and off."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_wisp_spirits_active"									            "Spirits"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_wisp_spirits_active_Description"						            "Surrounded by friendly spirits."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_skywrath_mage_shard_bonus_counter_lua"				            "Hero Shard Upgraded"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_skywrath_mage_shard_bonus_counter_lua_Description"	            "Everytime you cast abilities you gain +5 Intelligence and +1 Armor for 35 seconds. Stacks independently."
