		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_recipe_aeon_disk_lua"			                            "Recipe（Aeon Disk）"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_aeon_disk_lua"							                	"Aeon Disk"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aeon_disk_lua_Description"					                "<h1>Passive: Combo Breaker</h1> When you take damage and your health falls below %health_threshold_pct%%, a strong dispel is applied and you gain a %buff_duration% second buff that provides +%status_resistance%%% Status Resistance and causes all damage you deal and are dealt to be reduced to zero. Can trigger from creep damage."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aeon_disk_lua_lore"							                "A powerful artifact secretly smuggled out of the Ivory Nest many years ago. Many have come to believe it’s true."
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aeon_disk_lua_bonus_health"				                	"+$health"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aeon_disk_lua_bonus_mana"					                "+$mana"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_aeon_disk_lua_buff"							                "Combo Breaker"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_aeon_disk_lua_buff_Description"				                "All incoming and outgoing damage negated."

